# Omninuera
**Offer of Internship (AI Intern)**

Date: [Date]

Candidate: **[Candidate Full Name]**

Dear [Candidate Full Name],

We are pleased to offer you an internship with Omninuera (the "Company") for the position of **AI Intern**. This document summarizes the primary terms of your internship. This is a draft offer intended for review by Legal and HR and is editable.

---

## 1. Position and Scope
- Role: AI Intern.
- Duration: 3 months, commencing on **[Start Date]** and ending on the date three months thereafter, unless earlier terminated in accordance with this letter.
- Reporting Manager: **[Reporting Manager]**.
- Work Location: Fully remote. Candidate is based in Bengaluru.
- Employment Type: Internship (temporary engagement). This is a temporary, non-employee internship. You will receive a stipend (not a salary), and you are not entitled to employee benefits, except as explicitly provided in writing.

---

## 2. Working Hours
- Expected weekly commitment: **20–40 hours per week**, with flexible scheduling to accommodate remote work and academic commitments.
- Specific hours and deliverables will be agreed with your Reporting Manager.

---

## 3. Stipend
- Stipend amount: **INR 10,000 per month**.
- This amount is a stipend for the internship and does not constitute a salary or wages under applicable employment laws.
- Payment schedule: Monthly in arrears via bank transfer to the bank account details you provide (placeholder below).
- Bank details (placeholder): **[Bank Account Details: Account Name, Account Number, Bank Name, Branch, IFSC]**.

---

## 4. Key Responsibilities / Scope of Work
As an AI Intern, your responsibilities may include but are not limited to:
- Data collection, cleaning, and preparation for model training and evaluation.
- Running experiments with machine learning / deep learning models, including tuning and evaluation.
- Assisting in model development, benchmarking, and reproducibility of results.
- Preparing documentation of experiments, methodologies, and results.
- Collaborating with team members on research, code reviews, and knowledge sharing.
- Other reasonable tasks related to AI research and product development as assigned by the Reporting Manager.

---

## 5. Confidentiality and Intellectual Property
- Confidentiality: During and after the internship, you must keep confidential and not disclose any proprietary or confidential information of Omninuera. You agree to follow the Company’s confidentiality policies and procedures.
- IP Assignment: You agree that all inventions, discoveries, designs, works of authorship, or other intellectual property (collectively, “IP”) that you create, develop, or reduce to practice, whether alone or jointly with others, during the period of your internship and in connection with your internship activities, shall be the exclusive property of Omninuera. You hereby assign (or agree to assign) to Omninuera all rights, title, and interest in such IP and will execute any documents reasonably required to effectuate such assignment.
- If requested, you will sign the Company’s standard confidentiality and IP assignment agreement.

---

## 6. Termination / Early Exit
- Either party may terminate this internship for any reason by providing **one (1) week’s written notice** to the other party.
- Omninuera may terminate the internship immediately for cause (including but not limited to breach of confidentiality, gross misconduct, theft, falsification of records, or serious violation of Company policies).
- On termination, you must immediately return or destroy all Company property and confidential information in your possession.

---

## 7. Conditions of Offer
- This offer is subject to satisfactory completion of any required background verification and review for legal and regulatory compliance.
- This letter is not an employment contract nor does it create an obligation for continued engagement beyond the specified internship period.

---

## 8. Tax and Benefits
- You are responsible for any taxes or statutory contributions applicable to this stipend under Indian law.
- The stipend does not entitle you to employee benefits (such as health insurance, provident fund, or gratuity) unless expressly stated in writing.

---

## 9. Governing Law
- This offer and any disputes arising out of or related to it shall be governed by the laws of India. The courts in Bengaluru, India shall have exclusive jurisdiction.

---

## 10. Acceptance
If you wish to accept this offer, please sign and date below and return a scanned copy to the HR team. This offer is valid until [Offer Expiry Date] unless otherwise extended in writing.

